Robot is the default [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars|avatar]] in [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]]. Every new user logging into VRChat for the first time, starts out as this avatar.

==Appearance==
Robot is a simplistic grey humanoid Avatar. It has a floating head and its hands are especially accentuated, so that [[Special:MyLanguage/Finger tracking|finger tracking]] can be used with it.

